title: Stuck in the logging on ..... page
body: I am able to start the game before. I cannot play since I have moved to Switzerland. I have stopped played the game for few days, I am struggled and stuck on the logging on page. How can I solve currently, please?

replies.body: Your network settings would have changed and might not be able to access the authentication servers.  Go over the steps in the [connection issues](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) guide to help get this fixed up!  Let me know if you have any questions.
